job_history.work_description: Effective organizational, multi tasking, and prioritizing skills Excellent verbal, written, and interpersonal communication skills Proficient with proactively sourcing, acquiring, building, and maintaining relationships with customers and colleagues High motivation with ability to successfully meet individual and team goals Ability to work independently without supervision Basic Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, and Outlook) skills.

Experience leading or participating in events and activities for local networks or professional organizations, such as the chamber of commerce and professional business groups. Overseen the branch platform and teller side when management are off by making sure Customer Experience is top of mind at all times. Mitigating losses and Risks for the branch. Coaching in the moment by conducting bankers and tellers DBE's, and providing constructive feedback to my peers.

Manage the Teller's work flow to ensure success with daily cash balancing, building great rapport with customers, and meeting their referral and sales goals- all while maintaining an ethical and positive work environment for all. Requires little supervision and juggle a variety of tasks including exercising excellent customer service in all customer interactions and managing and resolving customer conflicts.

skills.name: Leadership
skills.explanation: Has experience leading teams and overseeing branch operations, mitigating losses and risks, and coaching peers, indicating strong proficiency in leadership.

skills.name: Customer Service
skills.explanation: Has extensive experience in customer-facing roles, ensuring customer experience is top of mind, resolving conflicts, and building great rapport with customers, indicating expert-level mastery.

skills.name: Communication
skills.explanation: Possesses excellent verbal, written, and interpersonal communication skills, which is essential for effective customer service and team collaboration, indicating strong proficiency.

skills.name: Time Management
skills.explanation: Has experience juggling multiple tasks, prioritizing, and meeting individual and team goals, suggesting strong proficiency in time management.

skills.name: Risk Management
skills.explanation: Has experience mitigating losses and risks for the branch, indicating a solid working proficiency in risk management.

skills.name: Microsoft Office
skills.explanation: Has basic skills in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, and Outlook), indicating some practical experience but limited depth.

skills.name: Sales
skills.explanation: Has experience meeting sales goals and building relationships with customers, indicating a solid working proficiency in sales.
